<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Carbon credits are largely a matter of baselin=
es. We talk about this a lot with trees. One classic way to get carbon cred=
its is by <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33116434=
.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDQ=
