<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Direct carbon capture technology =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0where you <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33116=
434.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2ZlYXR1cmVzLzIwMjMtMTAt=
